title: [Smuggling Tunnels, Passage]
description: Wooden beams, tumbled from the ceiling, litter the floor in one large heap.  A nest of termites has moved in, turning the pile into a writhing mass of slimy insectile bodies.  Powdered wood sprinkles the floor in clumps, further fodder for the disgusting little creatures.
paths: Obvious exits: northeast, east, south, southwest
